From [Add Newtonsoft.Json-based JSON format support](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/core/web-api/advanced/formatting?view=aspnetcore-3.0#add-newtonsoftjson-based-json-format-support)

```
services.AddControllers().AddNewtonsoftJson(options =&gt;
{
